-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Spring MVC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
designed around DispatcherServlet

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DispatcherServlet
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Takes a HTTP request and dispatches it to the
    right handler (@Controller) and the right view (JSP).
Provides out of the box resolution strategies
- view resolvers
- locale resolvers
- theme resolvers
- exception handlers

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# spring-boot-starter-web
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Auto configuration adds following features to the app
- static content support (html, css, js under /static)
- HttpMessageConverters (JSON)
- JSON serializers/deserializers
- Path matching & content negotiation (.pdf, .json, ?format=xml)
- error handling (/error, 404.html, etc.,
    @ExceptionHandler, @ControllerAdvice, ErrorPageRegistrar)
- template engine support (Thymeleaf etc. under /templates)
